org.jboss.jdeparser

Interface JClassDef

  • All Superinterfaces:
    JAnnotatable, JCommentable, JDocCommentable, JGenericDef
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    JAnonymousClassDef

    public interface JClassDef
extends JAnnotatable, JDocCommentable, JGenericDef
    A type definition, which can be a class, interface, annotation type, etc.
    Author:
    David M. Lloyd
